Nash-Betts%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20said%2C%20'In%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20can%20only%20see%20you%20doing%20this.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Nash-Betts%20decided%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%2C%20even%20though%20it%20required%20her%20to%20fly%20from%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rookie%3A%20Feds%26quot%3B%20to%20Georgia%2C%20where%20%26quot%3BOrigin%26quot%3B%20was%20filming%2C%20every%20weekend%20for%20about%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENash-Betts%20emphasized%20that%20the%20film%20is%20an%20indie%20project%2C%20and%20praised%20costar%20Aunjanue%20Ellis%20for%20her%20equally%20scrappy%20efforts%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC17U9o0u0E8%2F%3Figsh%3DMWY0cnhyZzh1Y28wbQ%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecampaign%20for%20the%20film%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20of%20an%20AMC%20theater%20as%20awards%20season%20kicks%20into%20high%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20an%20independent%20film.%20All%20grassroots%20efforts%20count%2C%20and%20we%20all%20have%20skin%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Nash-Betts%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20wonderful%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20reach%20the%20people%2C%20take%20it%20back%20to%20the%20streets.%20That's%20old%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20ethos%20Nash-Betts%20put%20into%20practice%20on%20the%20Emmys%20stage%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femmy-awards-2024-highlights-lowlights-in-memoriam-ally-mcbeal-cheers-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eher%20acceptance%20speech%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20when%20she%20not%20only%20thanked%20herself%20but%20also%20dedicated%20her%20award%20to%20%26quot%3Bevery%20black%20and%20brown%20woman%20who%20has%20gone%20unheard%20yet%20overpoliced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20artist%2C%20my%20job%20is%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%2C%20and%20baby%2C%20I'm%20gonna%20d