0morning%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20stopped%20from%20entering%20the%20state's%20well-known%20Batadrava%20Satra%20Temple%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Srimanta%20Sankardeva%2C%20an%20Assamese%20saint%20and%20scholar%20from%20the%2015th%20century%2C%20in%20Nagaon.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20registered%20protest%20by%20sitting%20on%20a%20dharna%20on%20the%20road%20in%20Nagaon%2C%20singing%20Raghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20stopped%20from%20continuing%20the%20footmarch%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20held%20a%20street%20corner%20meeting%20in%20neighbouring%20Morigaon%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20had%20urged%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20reconsider%20the%20route%20for%20his%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20potential%20clashes%20with%20the%20programmes%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20state%20alongside%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20invited%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20The%20invite%20went%20to%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20declined%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20politicisation%20of%20a%20religious%20event%20in%20an%20election%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20had%20made%20his%20stance%20clear%20vis-a-vis%20the%20Ram%20temple%20inauguration%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BNarendra%20Modi%20Function%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20made%20the%20January%2022%20function%20a%20completely%20political%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20function.%20It%20has%20become%20an%20RSS-BJP%20function.%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20go%20to%20a%20political%20function%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20around%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20and%20the%20RSS.%20We%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20whoever%20among%20our%20partners%20or%20our%20party%20would%20like%20to%20visit%20the%20Ram%20temple%20is%20welcome%20to%20do%20it.%20It%20is%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20visit%20(the%20temple)%20on%20January%2022.%20That%20this%20is%20a%20prime%20minister's%20function%20and%20an%20RSS%20function%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20attend%20it%20...%20it%20is%20not%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added%2C%20drawing%20brickbats%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20lives%20in%20a%20la-la%20world.%20He%20thinks%20everything%20he%20says%20is%20predicated%20on%20nobody%20understanding%20the%20truth%20and%20he%20can%20get%20away%20with%20these%20atrocious%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20censured%20all%20who%20declined%20the%20invite.%20Calling%20the%20leaders%20anti-Hindu%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20declared%20that%20they%20will%20get%20their%20punishment%20from%20the%20people%20at%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705930620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F10lisgro_himanta-sarma-1200-_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flets-not-talk-of-ravan-today-himanta-biswa-sarmas-swipe-at-rahul-gandhi-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-consecration-day-4910912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20today%20responded%20with%20a%20Ramayan%20reference%20when%20a%20reporter%20asked%20why%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20a%20temple%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flets-not-talk-of-ravan-today-himanta-biswa-sarmas-swipe-at-rahul-gandhi-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-consecration-day-4910912%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.n