e%2C%20in%20a%20police%20vehicle%20but%20they%20did%20not%20want%20him%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20yatra%2C%20in%20its%20ninth%20day%2C%20later%20resumed%20at%202%20pm%20and%20proceeded%20towards%20Morigaon%20before%20heading%20to%20Nongpoh%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20(January%2021)%2C%20Sarma%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20had%20urged%20Gandhi%20to%20visit%20the%20Batadrava%20Than%20after%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20like%20there%20is%20a%20competition%20between%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20Batadrava%20Than.%20That%20is%20not%20good%20for%20Assam.%20So%2C%20we%20request%20that%20we%20would%20like%20it%20if%20he%20goes%20to%20Batadrava%20Than%20after%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20programme%20is%20done.%20I%20would%20like%20that.%20Otherwise%20television%20channels%20will%20show%20the%20two%20in%20a%20two-window.%20But%20that%20two-window%20will%20go%20against%20the%20image%20of%20Assam.%20There%20is%20no%20competition%20and%20he%20should%20not%20come%20and%20create%20that%20competition.%20That%20will%20be%20sad%20for%20people%20of%20Assam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20supporters%20with%20saffron%20flags%20surrounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-rahul-gandhi-meets-protestors-blows-kisses-to-bjp-supporters-raising-slogans%5C%22%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20convoy%20and%20raised%20slogans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20allegedly%20attacked%20Assam%20Congress%20chief%20Bhupen%20Borah%20as%20well%20as%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%9C%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20'%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%