%20of%20the%20same%20agreement%2C%20two%20documents%20have%20been%20presented...it%20is%20a%2010%2C000%20square%20feet%20plot%20for%20which%20a%20transaction%20of%20Rs%209%20crore%20has%20been%20done.%20The%20second%20party%2C%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20gave%20his%20agreement%20to%20the%20purchase%20while%20his%20attorney%2C%20Rajesh%20Yadav%2C%20executed%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Big%20and%20Abhishek%2C%20several%20other%20A-listers%20and%20who's%20who%20of%20the%20Indian%20film%20and%20entertainment%20industry%2C%20including%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20Anupam%20Kher%2C%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Vicky%20Kaushal%2C%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20Subhash%20Ghai%20and%20Sonu%20Nigam%20were%20in%20attendance%20at%20the%20Pran%20Patishtha%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20saw%20the%20participation%20of%20about%208%2C000%20invitees%2C%20including%201%2C500-1%2C600%20eminent%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20ceremony%20unfolded%2C%20army%20choppers%20were%20pictured%20showering%20petals%20on%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20showered%20petals%20on%20workers%2C%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20construction%20team%20that%20shaped%20the%20grand%20Ramn%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20seen%20sprinkling%20flowers%20on%20the%20idol%20of%20Jatayu%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20premises%20and%20also%20offered%20prayers%20to%20Lord%20Shiva%20in%20Ayodhya%20Dham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20dignitaries%20invited%20to%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20is%20not%20only%20a%20moment%20of%20triumph%20after%20a%20prolonged%20struggle%20but%20also%20one%20of%20humility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20a%20moment%20of%20celebration%20for%20us%20all%20but%20also%20one%20to%20reflect%20the%20coming%20of%20age%20of%20the%20Indian%20society.%20This%20occasion%20is%20as%20much%20about%20triumph%20as%20it%20is%20about%20humility.%20The%20world%20is%20replete%20with%20instances%20of%20countries%20that%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20difficulties%20resolving%20historic%20wrongs%20and%20injustices.%20However%2C%20the%20way%20we%20untied%20the%20knots%20and%20resolved%20all%20outstanding%20issues%20gives%20us%20hope%20that%20our%20future%20is%20going%20to%20be%20more%20beautiful%20and%20fulfilling%20than%20our%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20said%20that%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20which%20some%20feared%20would%20set%20off%20a%20firestorm%2C%20now%20stands%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20peace%2C%20patience%2C%20harmony%20and%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20also%20a%20time%20when%20some%20people%20used%20to%20say%20'Ram%20Mandir%20bana%20toh%20aag%20lag%20jaegi'%20(the%20making%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20would%20set%20off%20a%20firestorm).%20Such%20people%20lacked%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20purity%20of%20our%20society%2C%20the%20spirit%20that%20binds%20us%20all.%20This%20majestic%20abode%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Lalla%20will%20now%20stand%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20peace%2C%20patience%2C%20mutual%20harmony%20and%20social%20unity.%20The%20construction%20of%20this%20temple%20did%20not%20set%20off%20a%20fire%20but%20exuded%20a%20positive%20energy%20that%20has%20been%20infectious%20for%20us%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20also%20testifies%20to%20a%20renewed%20national%20consciousness%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20his%20place%20in%20our%20everyday%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20was%20unveiled%20during%20the%20grand%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%2C%20which%20involved%20hour-long%20rituals%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edit