tion%20of%20an%20able%20and%20grand%20India.%20This%20is%20the%20expansion%20of%20consciousness%20from%20dev%20(God)%20to%20desh%20(country)%20and%20from%20Ram%20to%20Rashtra%20(nation)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENishad%20King%20Guh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20then%20referred%20to%20Nishad%20King%20Guh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20king%20of%20a%20tribal%20kingdom%20on%20the%20bank%20of%20Ganga.%20When%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Sita%20and%20Lakshman%20reached%20his%20kingdom%20after%20leaving%20Ayodhya%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Nishad%20king%20who%20helped%20them%20cross%20the%20river%2C%20starting%20a%20friendship%20that%20continues%20through%20the%20epic.%20When%20Lord%20Ram's%20brother%20Bharat%20set%20out%20in%20his%20search%2C%20the%20Nishad%20King%20had%20first%20suspected%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20attack%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20vowed%20to%20prevent%20him.%20On%20learning%20that%20Bharat%20was%20out%20to%20bring%20his%20elder%20brother%20back%2C%20the%20Nishad%20King%20welcomed%20him%20warmly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20way%20back%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%2014%20years%20of%20exile%2C%20Lord%20Ram%20did%20not%20forget%20to%20meet%20his%20friend%2C%20the%20Nishad%20King.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20friendship%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20the%20Nishad%20King%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20feeling%20of%20friendship%20between%20every%20Indian%20will%20form%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20grand%20India.%20This%20is%20the%20expansion%20of%20consciousness%20from%20dev%20(God)%20to%20desh%20(country)%20and%20from%20Ram%20to%20Rashtra%20(nation)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Squirrel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20squirrel%20features%20in%20Ramayan%20at%20the%20point%20when%20monkeys%20backing%20Lord%20Ram%20are%20building%20a%20bridge%20across%20the%20sea%20to%20reach%20Lanka%20to%20take%20on%20Ravan.%20As%20Hanuman%20and%20others%20in%20the%20monkey%20army%20lifted%20boulders%20and%20dropped%20them%20into%20the%20water%2C%20a%20squirrel%20worked%20alongside%2C%20carrying%20pebbles%20in%20its%20mouth%20and%20dropping%20them%20into%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Hanuman%20told%20the%20squirrel%20that%20it%20was%20getting%20in%20its%20way.%20When%20the%20squirrel%20replied%20that%20it%20was%20doing%20its%20bit%20to%20help%20build%20the%20bridge%2C%20the%20monkeys%20started%20laughing.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20came%20forward%20and%20told%20them%20to%20see%20the%20love%20in%20the%20squirrel's%20heart.%20Lord%20Ram%20said%20that%20while%20the%20monkeys%20are%20dropping%20huge%20boulders%20into%20the%20ocean%2C%20the%20pebbles%20brought%20by%20small%20animals%20like%20the%20squirrel%20were%20filling%20the%20gaps.%20The%20monkeys%2C%20he%20said%2C%20should%20not%20make%20fun%20of%20the%20weak%20and%20small%20and%20acknowledge%20their%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monkeys%20were%20ashamed.%20Lord%20Ram%20then%20thanked%20the%20squirrel%20and%20patted%20its%20back.%20The%20Ramayan%20says%20the%20stripes%20on%20a%20squirrel's%20back%20came%20from%20the%20Lord's%20pat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20this%20story%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20despair%20in%20the%20country%20today.%20%26quot%3BThose%20thinking%2C%20'I%20am%20very%20ordinary'%20must%20think%20of%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20squirrel.%20It%20will%20remove%20such%20hesitations%20and%20teach%20us%20that%20every%20effort%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20has%20its%20own%20strength.%20It%20is%20everyone's%20efforts%20that%20will%20form%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20grand%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-12%2Fjatayu-park_65