%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3ERam%20aa%20gaye%20%F0%9F%9A%A9%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FI880rco1Sd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FI880rco1Sd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20(%40KanganaTeam)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKanganaTeam%2Fstatus%2F1749340109466710057%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20the%20actor%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20to%20motivate%20people%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20broom%20by%20participating%20in%20this%20cleanliness%20drive.%20The%20city%20has%20been%20beautified%20and%20has%20a%20festive%20look%20about%20it%20going%20into%20the%20inauguration%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnificent%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Mandir%20is%20constructed%20in%20traditional%20Nagara%20style.%20Its%20length%20(east-west)%20is%20380%20feet%3B%20width%20is%20250%20feet%20and%20height%20is%20161%20feet%3B%20and%20is%20supported%20by%20a%20total%20of%20392%20pillars%20and%2044%20doors.%20The%20pillars%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20temple%20showcase%20intricately%20sculpted%20depictions%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20gods%2C%20and%20goddesses.%20In%20the%20main%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20the%20childhood%20form%20of%20Bhagwan%20Shri%20Ram%20(Ram%20Lalla)%20has%20been%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20entrance%20to%20the%20Mandir%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%2C%20which%20can%20be%20approached%20by%20ascending%2032%20stairs%20through%20the%20Singh%20Dwar.%20There%20are%20a%20total%20of%20five%20Mandaps%20(Halls)%20in%20the%20Mandir%20-%20Nritya%20Mandap%2C%20Rang%20Mandap%2C%20Sabha%20Mandap%2C%20Prathana%20Mandap%20and%20Kirtan%20Mandap.%20Near%20the%20Mandir%20is%20a%20historic%20Well%20(Sita%20koop)%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20ancient%20era.%20In%20the%20southwestern%20part%20of%20the%20Mandir%20complex%2C%20at%20Kuber%20Tila%2C%20the%20anci