ent%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-motors-to-commence-ev-production-at-sanand-plant-from-april-2024-124012200593_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-motors-to-commence-ev-production-at-sanand-plant-from-april-2024-124012200593_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-motors-to-commence-ev-production-at-sanand-plant-from-april-2024-124012200593_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Making%20of%20a%20Temple%20State%20and%20What%20We%20have%20Done%20to%20Deserve%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22161854%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.26.21-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20message%20about%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20celebration%20popped%20up%20on%20my%20WhatsApp%20messages%20today%20from%20a%20BJP-Bajrang%20Dal%20member%2C%20who%20catapulted%20to%20fame%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Shamli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20whipping%20a%20Muslim%20nearly%20to%20death.%20The%20Muslim%20who%20was%20beaten%20had%20allegedly%20stolen%20a%20calf%20to%20sell%20as%20meat.%20The%20whipping%20was%20of%20course%20a%20public%20performance%2C%20done%20to%20scale%20with%20a%20fawning%20Hindu%20audience.%20That%20same%20man%20who%20I%20will%20not%20name%20only%20so%20he%20does%20not%20draw%20more%20mileage%20from%20this%2C%20sent%20out%20a%20message%20saying%20that%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20is%20hereby%20instructed%20to%20close%20all%20meat%20and%20liquor%20shops%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20celebration%20of%20Hindus%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98national%20mandir%E2%80%99%2C%20there%20is%20theatrics%20at%20play%20that%20we%20must%20not%20miss.%20What%20pray%20is%20a%20national%20temple%3F%20Do%20we%20have%20a%20national%20mosque%20or%20was%20that%20destroyed%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20in%20order%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20mob%3F%20Why%20is%20every%20district%20administration%20making%20rules%20and%20being%20given%20instructions%20as%20if%20the%20celebration%20is%20intertwined%20with%20statecraft%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20morphing%20of%20religion%20with%20state%20that%20the%20bigoted%20media%20is%20amplifying%20and%20the%20secular%20media%20glossing%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20this%2022-year-old%20papering%20over%20the%20history%20of%20hate%20is%20another%20big%20black%20hole%20in%20our%20politics%20that%20has%20brought%20us%20to%20this%20disturbing%20moment.%20We%20think%20ultra-nationalism%20is%20a%20big%20problem%20without%20looking%20at%20the%20second%20part%20of%20this%20hyphenated%20word%20%E2%80%93%20nationalism.%20We%20think%20that%20if%20we%20just%20counter%20the%20idea%20of%20religious%20nationalism%20and%20identity%20with%20a%20secular%20Indian-ness%2C%20we%20have%20an%20ideological%20counter.%20And%20all%20we%20need%20to%20do%20is%20spread%20it%20around%20better.%20That%20however%20is%20where%20we%20have%20failed%20to%20look%20at%20the%20real%20shape%20and%20size%20of%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20proper%20answers%2C%20I%20suggest%20we%20take%20a%20look%20beyond%20India%2C%20at%20ultra-nationalisms%20everywhere.%20And%20that%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20see.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20the%20US%2C%20poised%20at%20the%20nightmarish%20possibility%20of%20a%20second%20innings%20for%20Donald%20Trump.%20Or%20at%20the%20new%20Argentinian%20President%20Javier%20Milei%20who%20dressed%20in%20super-hero%20costumes%20and%20went%20around%20campaigning%20with%20a%20chainsaw%20to%20%E2%80%98cut%20corruption%E2%80%99.%20Why%20is%20there%20a%20turn%20towards%20the%20far%20right%20around%20the%20world%2C%20even%20in%20countries%20that%20did%20not%20go%20through%20a%20Partition%20or%20a%20Mandir%20movement%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20not%20in%20the%20word%20ultra%20but%20in%20nationalism.%20We%20have%20been%20looking%20at%20the%20wrong%20part%20of%20the%20word%20all%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22145957%2FIMG-20240121-WA0036.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22145957%2FIMG-20240121-WA0036.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22145957%2FIMG-20240121-WA0036-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693993%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJavier%20Milei%20during%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20December%201992%2C%20we%20have%20been%20distracted%20by%20the%20histrionics%20of%20the%20far%20right%20and%20not%20looked%20at%20our%20own%20part%20in%20this%20game.%20The%20problem%20is%20much%20deeper%20than%20the%20extreme%20expression%20of%20nationalism%20as%20a%20homogenous%20religious%20majoritarianism.%20The%20problem%20is%20in%20our%20failure%20to%20look%20at%20the%20word%20nationalism%20itself%20as%20a%20homogenising%20project%2C%20where%20all%20we%20have%20in%20terms%20of%20manoeuvring%20space%20is%20to%20say%20we%20have%20greater%20or%20lower%20levels%20of%20tolerance%20of%20difference%20than%20the%20next%20person.%20If%20we%20say%20we%20are%20okay%20with%20accommodating%20difference%2C%20that%20we%20would%20be%20fine%20if%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20but%20of%20Italian%20birth%20became%20our%20prime%20minister%20the%20same%20way%20as%20Rishi%20Sunak%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20UK%2C%20I%20would%20like%20us%20to%20take%20our%20imagination%20a%20lot%20farther.%20Would%20we%20be%20able%20to%20imagine%20an%20Eskimo%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20Netherlands%20or%20a%20Japanese%20looking%20person%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Nigeria%3F%20If%20anyone%20with%20any%20sort%20of%20face%20and%20ethnicity%20can%20govern%20any%20country%20then%20what%20is%20nationalism%3F%20And%20if%20there%20is%20a%20limit%20to%20who%20can%20govern%20what%20place%20then%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20nationalism%20by%20definition%20is%20the%20politics%20of%20ethnic%20inclusion%20and%20exclusion%20to%20one%20degree%20or%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20get%20our%20definition%20of%20nationalism%20and%20by%20extension%20democracy%20and%20freedom%20from%20the%20West%2C%20then%20the%20problem%20lies%20right%20there.%20If%20the%20West%20is%20such%20an%20inclusive%20social%20construct%2C%20why%20did%20Europe%20send%20Polish%20and%20Russian%20and%20French%20and%20English%20Jews%20of%20these%20respective%20nationalities%20to%20Palestinian%20territories%20after%20World%20War%202%2C%20to%20form%20the%20nation%20of%20Israel%3F%20This%20is%20a%20question%20the%20political%20scientist%20Mahmood%20Mamdani%20asks%20in%20his%20seminal%20book%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ENeither%20Settler%20nor%20Native%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20answer%20he%20provides%20is%20equally%20chilling.%20His%20book%20reminds%20us%20that%20Western%20Europe%20was%20antisemitic%20and%20therefore%20wanted%20Jews%20to%20be%20housed%20elsewhere%2C%20out%20of%20sight%20of%20the%20Western%2FChristian%20world.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20there%20could%20not%20be%20a%20conception%20of%20a%20post%20World%20War%202%20Poland%20or%20France%20composed%20of%20Christians%2C%20Jews%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Moors%20and%20other%20religions.%20The%20place%20for%20Jews%20was%20elsewhere%20and%20as%20Europe%20is%20increasingly%20showing%20us%2C%20the%20place%20for%20Muslims%2C%20Romas%2C%20Armenians%2C%20all%20sorts%20of%20%E2%80%98different%E2%80%99%20people%20is%20also%20elsewhere.%20Nationalism%20meant%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20sameness%20in%20Europe.%20If%20you%20were%20different%2C%20please%20go%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Power%20Is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20His%20Faith%2C%20His%20Trade'%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpower-is-modis-ram-his-faith-his-trade%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Power%20Is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20His%20Faith%2C%20His%20Trade%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20want%20to%20%E2%80%98un-Babri%E2%80%99%20our%20lives%2C%20we%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20big%20rock%20we%E2%80%99re%20sitting%20under%20%E2%80%93%20nationalism.%20Who%20are%20we%3F%20Aryan%3F%20Dravidian%3F%20Mughal%3F%20Mixed%3F%20How%20mixed%3F%20Can%20we%20mainstream%20people%20from%20Manipur%20and%20Arunachal%20with%20ethnicities%20that%20go%20back%20to%20Burmese%20and%20other%20East%20Asian%20racial%20types%3F%20Can%20we%20mainstream%20the%20Siddis%20that%20are%20of%20African%20descent%3F%20Who%20is%20Indian%3F%20Who%20gets%20left%20out%3F%20There%E2%80%99s%20much%20light%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20shone%20on%20these%20questions%20by%20the%20anthropologist%20who%20leads%20the%20way%20on%20these%20questions%20of%20difference%2C%20Arjun%20Appadurai.%20Writing%20soon%20after%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20in%20India%20and%20the%20twin%20towers%20in%20America%2C%20Appadurai%20pointed%20out%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EFear%20of%20Small%20Numbers%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20our%20globalised%20Islamophobia%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20displaced%20nationalism.%20When%20world%20markets%20had%20broken%20free%20from%20national%20boundaries%2C%20nationalism%20got%20frozen%20and%20confined%20to%20smaller%20spaces%20and%20that%20made%20the%20majority%20live%20in%20permanent%20fear%20of%20minorities%20that%20showed%20up%20as%20different%20and%20asked%20questions%20of%20who%20belonged%20and%20who%20did%20not.%20Belonging%20becomes%20a%20problem%20when%20everything%20is%20everywhere%20and%20nothing%20stands%20out%20as%20yours%20any%20more.%20When%20everyone%20has%20an%20iPhone%20and%20your%20neighbour%20in%20Delhi%20has%20the%20same%20holiday%20in%20Hungary%20as%20your%20business%20partner%20in%20London%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20greater%20need%20to%20underline%20your%20roots%20and%20point%20out%20what%20makes%20you%20YOU.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20ultras%20start%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20it%20is%20even%20harder%20in%20a%20world%20where%20social%20media%20makes%20even%20more%20mush%20of%20everything%20and%20spreads%20every%20idea%20and%20experience%20around%20as%20smoothly%20as%20butter.%20And%20so%20we%20turn%20more%20loudly%20and%20violently%20to%20our%20pet%20themes%20of%20us%20and%20them%2C%20we%20the%20mainstream%20and%20they%20the%20outcastes.%20And%20these%20little%20hysterical%20victories%20define%20us%20more%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21191409%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-4.19.49-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221071%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21191409%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-4.19.49-PM.jpeg%201071w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21191409%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-4.19.49-PM-300x228.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21191409%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-4.19.49-PM-1024x778.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693912%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22814%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Ram%20mandir%20on%20