Emade%20a%20show%20of%20inviting%20the%20two%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20on%20Monday%20was%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-provocateur-in-chief-l-k-advani%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20founded%20in%201980%20and%20Advani%20assumed%20leadership%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20in%201984%20before%20becoming%20party%20president%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20the%20BJP%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpast-continuous-the-birth-of-the-ram-mandir-agitation%5C%22%3E%C2%A0announced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20on%20the%20land%20where%20they%20believed%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20born%20%E2%80%93%20and%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20had%20stood%20for%20over%20400%20years%20%E2%80%93%20was%20its%20key%20political%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20autumn%20of%201990%2C%20Advani%20launched%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Erath%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Somnath%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20which%20was%20to%20stir%20up%20support%20for%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20at%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20mosque%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Shiv%20temple%20had%20stood%20in%20Somnath%20since%20at%20least%20the%206th%C2%A0%C2%A0century%20CE.%20It%20was%20demolished%20and%20reconstructed%20several%20times%20over%20the%20centuries.%20The%20last%20demolition%20came%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20in%201665.%C2%A0It%20lay%20in%20ruins%20until%201950%20when%20its%20reconstruction%20began%20under%20the%20prime%20ministership%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20beginning%20the%20yatra%20at%20Somnath%20and%20ending%20in%20Ayodhya%20thus%20had%20a%20very%20powerful%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0symbolic%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0value%20of%20%E2%80%98reclaiming%E2%80%99%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20was%20done%20in%20Somnath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20in%20his%202008%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcourtneylaportecarm.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fmy-country-my-life-by-lk-advani-foreward-by-atal-bihari-vajpayee.pdf%5C%22%3Ebook%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMy%20Country%20My%20Life%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20choice%20of%20Somnath%20as%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eyatra%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0had%20a%20powerful%20symbolic%20value%2C%20made%20evident%20by%20repeated%20references%20to%20it%20as%20the%20target%20of%20Muslim%20tyranny%20against%20the%20Hindus%E2%80%A6The%20intention%20was%20to%20contextualise%20Ayodhya%20in%20the%20historical%20lineage%20of%20Muslim%20aggression%20and%20then%20to%20seek%20legitimacy%20for%20Mandir%20movement%20by%20drawing%20a%20parallel.%20The%20parallel%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20drew%20was%20with%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20Somnath%20temple.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra%20made%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20not%20carrying%20a%20message%20of%20peace.%20Pictures%20of%20him%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0carrying%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20axe%2C%20a%20sword%20and%20a%20bow%20and%20arrow%20also%20emerged.%20Workers%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20pasted%20posters%20along%20the%20route%20of%20the%20yatra%20of%20the%20proposed%20temple%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3Etreachery%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20course%20of%20the%20yatra%20there%20was%20large%20scale%20violence%2C%20rioting%20and%20killings.%20Advani%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20finally%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flalu-yadav-on-why-and-how-he-arrested-lk-advani-on-october-23-1990-1784734%5C%22%3E%C2%A0stopped%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20arrested%20by%20the%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav-led%20Bihar%20government%20in%20Samastipur%20in%20October%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Advani%2C%20thousands%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0managed%20to%20reach%20Ayodhya%20where%2020%20of%20them%20were%20killed%20after%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20a%20mob%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0led%20by%20a%20coterie%20of%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20were%20led%20by%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705915585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-who-led-ram-janmabhoomi-movement-skips-temple-consecration-citing-extreme-cold%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20had%20reportedly%20told%20him%20and%20his%20colleague%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-who-led-ram-janmabhoomi-movement-skips-temple-consecration-citing-extreme-cold%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20Pakistan%20universities%20shut%20over%20security%20threats%3A%20Police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705915429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107051152%2Cimgsize-1956426.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2