e%20have%20somebody%20who%20is%20acting%20like%20the%20king%20and%20has%20announced%20that%20divinity%20is%20passing%20through%20him%20or%20he%20is%20chosen%20by%20God%2C%20by%20the%20divine%20voice%20to%20perform%20this%20ceremony.%20This%20is%20a%20total%20subsumption%20of%20religion%20by%20politics.%20The%20line%20between%20the%20religion%20and%20the%20state%20has%20been%20broken%20down%20and%20is%20breaking%20down%20entirely%20at%20the%20initiative%20of%20the%20state%20which%20is%20dictating%20how%20religion%20and%20religious%20ceremonies%20are%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20political%20scientist%20Rajeev%20Bhargava%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modi-in-ram-temple-pran-prathishtha-end-of-secularism-as-distance-between-state-and-religion%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22134741%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.55.55-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22134741%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.55.55-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22134741%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.55.55-PM-300x137.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22134741%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.55.55-PM-1024x466.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22546%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%2C%20UP%20governor%20Anandiben%20Patel%20and%20others%20at%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20DD%20News%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20prayers%2C%20the%20priests%20and%20political%20leaders%20who%20were%20involved%20stepped%20out%20to%20the%20large%20crowd%20of%20invited%20guests%20in%20the%20temple%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20Dev%20Giri%20Ji%20Maharaj%2C%20who%20is%20treasurer-trustee%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janambhumi%20Tirth%20Kshetra%20Trust%2C%20said%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20devotion%20to%20rites%20reminds%20him%20of%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20one%20other%20king%20%E2%80%93%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20the%20rituals%20Modi%20has%20maintained%20ahead%20of%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20including%20fasting%20and%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20he%20said%20he%20%E2%80%9Creconfirmed%E2%80%9D%20from%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20mother%20that%20this%20is%20a%20habit%20he%20has%20had%20for%2040%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20down%20at%20several%20points%2C%20Govind%20Dev%20also%20cited%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20climate%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20day%20without%20elaborating%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20said%20it%20is%20as%20if%20we%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20Treta%20Yug%20%E2%80%93%20the%20second%20best%20of%20the%20four%20mythical%20slots%20of%20time%20observed%20in%20Hinduism.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20a%20nation%20put%20in%20so%20much%20effort%20over%20such%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20to%20get%20a%20temple%20in%20this%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adityanath.%20He%20spoke%20of%20%E2%80%9Csacrifices%E2%80%9D%20Hindus%20have%20made%2C%20apparently%20coming%20together%20across%20caste%20and%20community%2C%20to%20make%20this%20temple%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20sacrifice%20has%20borne%20fruit%20because%20the%20temple%20was%20built%20exactly%20where%20we%20had%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20built%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2C%20using%20the%20famous%20Hindi%20phrase%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EMandir%20wahi%20banayenge%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20popularised%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992%20and%20afterwards.%20He%20credited%20Modi%20with%20this%20becoming%20possible%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20with%20his%20election%20win%20in%202014%20that%20Hindus%20were%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20holy%20land%20will%20be%20the%20cultural%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20Adityanath%20claimed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20double%20engine%20government%20has%20made%20all%20dreams%20of%20Ayodhya%20real%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20listing%20all%20the%20avenues%20in%20which%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Union%20and%20his%2C%20in%20the%20state%2C%20have%20apparently%20made%20the%20city%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20also%20spoke%20of%20the%20stringent%20vows%20kept%20by%20Narendra%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20an%20ascetic%2C%20I%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%E2%80%9DRam%20Lalla%20has%20come%20to%20Ayodhya.%20Why%20did%20he%20go%20from%20Ayodhya%3F%20Ayodhya%20is%20that%20land%20where%20there%20is%20no%20confusion%2C%20no%20strife.%20After%20his%2014-year-exile%2C%20Ram%20returned%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%20solving%20the%20strife%20of%20the%20world.%20Now%2C%20he%20has%20returned%20after%20500%20years%E2%80%A6This%20history%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20whoever%20makes%20sacrifices%20for%20Ram%20Rajya%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20their%20worries%20go%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagwat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagwat%20appeared%20to%20stress%20on%20duty%2C%20in%20line%20with%20what%20the%20government%20has%20also%20espoused.%20He%20then%20quoted%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20on%20greed%20and%20discipline.%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705910842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-con