l%20witnesses%20like%20Bano%20were%20informed%20in%20December%202023%20that%20the%20police%20is%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2F02-riots-guj-revokes-security-of-witnesses-former-judge%2Farticleshow%2F106359690.cms%5C%22%3Ewithdraw%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20security%20cover.%20Many%20such%20witnesses%20were%20in%20the%20protected%20persons%20category%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%2015%20years%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20special%20investigation%20team%20formed%20a%20witness%20protection%20cell%20for%20the%20complainants%2Fwitnesses%20of%20the%202002%20riots.%20The%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20now%20withdrawn%20security%20cover%20of%20various%20witnesses%2C%20lawyers%20of%20victims%20and%20even%20a%20judge%20who%20convicted%2032%20accused%20in%20the%20Naroda%20Patiya%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fheadlines-today-top-stories%2Fstory%2Fgujarat-hc-designates-nine-judges-for-trial-in-2002-gujarat-riot-cases-46884-2009-05-07%5C%22%3Erecommended%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20SIT%20must%20form%20a%20special%20witness%20protection%20cell%20considering%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20the%20nine%20cases%20that%20it%20was%20dealing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnprotected%2C%20uncertain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Abdul%20Hameed%20Sheikh%20lives%20in%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20Citizen%20Nagar%2C%20an%20area%20which%20is%20particularly%20distinguishable%20because%20of%20its%20rugged%20roads%2C%20worn%20out%20signboards%2C%20overwhelming%20stench%20of%20chemicals%20and%20heaps%20of%20garbage%20which%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20life%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20area.%20Citizen%20Nagar%20houses%20more%20than%2050%20Muslim%20families%20who%20were%20displaced%20in%20the%202002%20riots%20and%20have%20been%20living%20here%20for%20the%20past%2022%20year