3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20today%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20campaign%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%2016th%20century%20mosque%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%94%20built%20in%201528%20by%20Mir%20Baqi%2C%20commander%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Babur%20%E2%80%94%20by%20kar%20sevaks%20belonging%20to%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20outfits%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%20The%20demolition%2C%20which%20happened%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20concerted%20Hindutva%20movement%2C%20resulted%20in%20communal%20riots%20over%20months%2C%20which%20led%20to%20over%202%2C000%20deaths.%20The%20Babri%20Masjid%20has%20been%20a%20contested%20site%20since%201885%20as%20religious%20leaders%20and%20Hindutva%20outfits%20considered%20it%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20or%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20fight%20ensued%20in%201950%20when%20Gopal%20Visharad%20Sharma%20approached%20the%20Faizabad%20district%20court%20for%20the%20right%20to%20worship%20idols%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20which%20were%20placed%20there%20in%201949.%20On%20September%2030%2C%202010%2C%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20in%20a%202%3A1%20majority%2C%20ruled%20a%20three-way%20division%20of%20the%20disputed%20area%20between%20the%20Sunni%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20the%20Nirmohi%20Akhara%2C%20and%20Ram%20Lalla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20the%20entire%202.77%20acres%20of%20disputed%20land%20to%20deity%20Ram%20Lalla%20and%20directed%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20allot%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20Muslims%20for%20building%20a%20mosque.%20Though%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20referred%20to%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20demolition%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20egregious%20violation%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20verdict%20was%20criticised%20for%20accepting%20the%20logic%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfaith%20over%20fact%E2%80%9D%20and%20granting%20legal%20possession%20of%20land%20to%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fflix%2Fmalayalam-actors-directors-share-constitution-preamble-on-ram-temple-inauguration-day%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20News%20Minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705905772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22121142%2F1595847102_image-0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmalayalam-actors-directors-share-constitution-preamble-on-ram-temple-inauguration-day%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20is%20a%20reminder%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20day%20the%20BJP%20is%20seen%20to%20have%20fulfilled%20one%20of%20its%20most%20strident%20Hindutva%20promises%20%E2%80%94%20of%20the%20secular%2C%20socialist%2C%20and%20democratic%20values%20enshrined%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmalayalam-actors-directors-share-constitution-preamble-on-ram-temple-inauguration-day%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sony-Zee%20merger%20timeline%3A%20How%20leadership%20dispute%20ended%20the%20%2410%20bn%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705905737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-10%2F26%2Ffull%2F1666801916-3358.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsony-zee-merger-timeline-how-leadership-dispute-ended-the-10-bn-deal-124012200258_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sony%20Group%20Corp%20has%20called%20off%20its%20merger%20with%20Zee%20after%20nearly%20two%20years%20of%20negotiating%20the%20%2410%20billi