on-upcoming-elections-13053759%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Power%20Is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20His%20Faith%2C%20His%20Trade'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150907%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVaranasi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mughal%20prince%20Dara%20Shikoh%20granted%20the%20patta%2C%20or%20deed%2C%20for%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20to%20the%20forefathers%20of%20mahant%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Tiwari%20in%20the%2017th%20century.%20Since%20then%2C%20over%2010%20generations%2C%20his%20family%20oversaw%20the%20ritual%20tradition%20of%20the%20temple%20until%2C%20in%201983%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20deprived%20them%20of%20administrative%20powers.%20The%20rituals%20followed%20there%20are%20largely%20still%20those%20the%20Tiwaris%20determined%2C%20although%20alterations%20have%20been%20made%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20was%20a%20strident%20critic%20of%20the%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20Corridor%2C%20a%20pet%20project%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20after%20demolishing%20several%20ancient%20temples%20housing%20an%20estimated%20286%20shivlings.%20These%20were%20uprooted%20and%20thrown%20away%3B%20many%20broke%3B%20only%20146%20could%20be%20recovered%20and%20are%20stored%20at%20the%20police%20station%20of%20Lanka%2C%20a%20locality%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20where%20their%20worship%20is%20still%20carried%20out%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demolition%20deeply%20upset%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20often%20expressed%20his%20angst%20and%20anger%20at%20the%20mindless%20remaking%20of%20Varanasi%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20spaces.%20But%20that%20was%20in%20the%20past%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20believing%20Tiwari%20would%20have%20forgiven%20Modi%20amidst%20the%20extraordinary%20and%20orchestrated%20buzz%20over%20the%20idol%20consecration%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20projected%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20civilisational%20resurrection%E2%80%9D.%20Would%20he%2C%20like%20many%2C%20be%20celebrating%20January%2022%20in%20a%20special%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20attachment%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20event%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20one.%20It%20is%20an%20event%20for%20implementing%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20says.%20He%20promptly%20asks%3A%20Would%20I%20expect%20him%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20religious%20event%20sponsored%20by%2C%20say%2C%20a%20film%20star%3F%20Today%E2%80%99s%20event%20is%20no%20different%2C%20for%20it%20has%20been%20organised%20to%20feed%20the%20vanity%20of%20Modi%2C%20the%20superstar%20of%20Indian%20politics%2C%20not%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20society%E2%80%99s%20spiritual%20stirrings%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Looking%20Into%20Ayodhya's%20Ongoing%20Statue%20Politics%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flooking-into-ayodhyas-ongoing-statue-politics%5C%22%3ELooking%20Into%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Ongoing%20Statue%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPast%20prime%20ministers%2C%20too%2C%20visited%20temples%2C%20most%20notably%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20never%20were%20posters%20bearing%20their%20pictures%20found%20in%20and%20around%20temples.%20This%20has%20changed%2C%20rues%20Tiwari%2C%20for%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20Vishwanath%20Temple%2C%20a%20cutout%20of%20his%20was%20installed%20at%20its%20gates.%20Forget%20this%2C%20a%20religious%20rule%20will%20be%20violated%20by%20organising%20the%20ceremony%20of%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20giving%20life%20to%20the%20idol%2C%20in%20a%20temple%20still%20under%20construction%2C%20a%20point%20recently%20made%20by%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20I%20read%20the%20design%20behind%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20sacred%20rule%2C%20asks%20Tiwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20logical%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%20and%20inaugurate%20the%20temple%20on%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20the%20day%20he%20was%20born%2C%20which%20this%20year%20falls%20on%20April%2016.%20But%2C%20by%20then%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20would%20be%20underway%20and%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CModi%20wants%20to%20use%20Ram%20to%20gather%20votes.%20Power%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20his%20faith%2C%20his%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20explains%20the%20hurry%20to%20organise%20the%20pran%20pratishtha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20worries%20over%20the%20disregard%2C%20even%20contempt%2C%20shown%20in%20reimagining%20India%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20spaces%2C%20restructuring%20them%20in%20the%20manner%20of%20malls%2C%20where%20people%20go%20to%20make%20purchases%20and%20spend%20fun%20time%2C%20or%20turn%20them%20into%20tourist%20hubs.%20Both%20are%20attempts%20at%20commercially%20exploiting%20the%20sacred%2C%20not%20at%20evoking%20devotion%20for%20God%20among%20visitors.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20mall%2C%20not%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya.%20The%20first%20such%20mall%20to%20be%20built%20was%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple.%20The%20third%20one%20will%20come%20up%20at%20Mathura%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%2085vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150816%2Fimage0-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150816%2Fimage0-1.jpeg%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150816%2Fimage0-1-300x211.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22379%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMahant%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Tiwari.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20over%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20reflects%20the%20battle%20over%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20the%20eternal%20order%20of%20those%20now%20known%20as%20Hindu.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20is%20seeking%20to%20wrest%20from%20%3Cem%3Eacharyas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20religious%20preceptors%2C%20the%20power%20to%20define%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20its%20principles%2C%20its%20rules%20and%2C%20in%20the%20future%2C%20even%20what%20texts%20constitute%20the%20scriptures%20of%20Hindus.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20attempt%20to%20appropriate%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20goaded%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20into%20speaking%20against%20the%20January%2022%20inauguration%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20battle%20to%20control%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20has%20split%20the%20acharyas.%20There%20are%20those%20who%20owe%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Sangh%2C%20not%20to%20the%20dharma.%20Tiwari%20cites%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Varanasi-based%20astrologer%20who%20chose%20January%2022%20as%20the%20auspicious%20day%20for%20the%20ceremony%20of%20pran%20pratishtha%2C%20although%20he%20would%20have%20known%20it%20could%20not%20be%20done%20in%20a%20half-built%20temple.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20benefits%20for%20him%2C%20as%20there%20will%20be%20for%20those%20whom%20the%20Sangh%20will%20place%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20to%20carry%20out%20rituals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Indian%20Civilisation%20Is%20Being%20Disrobed%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Ram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Findian-civilisation-is-being-disrobed-in-the-city-of-ram%5C%22%3EIndian%20Civilisation%20Is%20Being%20Disrobed%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20temporal%20and%20the%20spiritual.%20The%20Sangh%20wants%20to%20acquire%20religious%20power%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20political%20heft.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20this%20happens%2C%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20control%20over%20our%20samaj%20would%20be%20complete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20predicts.%20The%20Sangh%20seems%20set%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal%2C%20I%20said%2C%20given%20the%20public%20support%20for%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CUntruth%20is%20always%20more%20alluring%20than%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20responds.%20He%20lists%20the%2010%20values%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20such%20as%20to%20tell%20the%20truth%2C%20eschew%20arrogance%20and%20anger%2C%20cultivate%20forbearance%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20values%20are%20declining%2C%20none%20of%20these%20is%20embodied%20by%20Modi%2C%20who%20is%20turning%20us%20into%20fanatics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20recites%20verses%20predicting%20that%20Bhagwan%20would%20send%20his%20avatar%20whenever%20the%20fundamental%20values%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20erode%20and%20the%20Hindu%20society%20deteriorates%20morally.%20Today%2C%20though%2C%20Tiwari%20will%20hope%20that%20God%20bestows%20wisdom%20on%20people%20so%20they%20can%20distinguish%20untruth%20from%20truth%2C%20and%20comprehend%20that%20the%20display%20of%20devotion%20for%20Ram%20today%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20harvest%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fajaz-ashraf%5C%22%3EAjaz%20Ashraf%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705887047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150907%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.10-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpower-is-modis-ram-his-faith-his-trade%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mahant%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Tiwari%20of%20Varanasi%20worries%20over%20the%20disregard%2C%20even%20contempt%2C%20shown%20i