0former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20in%20Nashik%20where%20he%20will%20offer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fuddhav-thackeray-gets-ram-mandir-invite-speed-post-sanjay-rauts-ravan-swipe-at-bjp-2491620-2024-01-21%5C%22%3Eprayers%20at%20the%20Kalaram%20Temple.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20said%20that%20while%20the%20political%20discourse%20might%20be%20centred%20around%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20other%20political%20parties%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20on%20the%20Ayodhya%20title%20suit%20was%20based%20on%20a%20certain%20legal%20technicality.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20subscribe%20to%20Hindutva%20claims.%20If%20you%20read%20the%20judgement%2C%20you%20find%20that%20the%20court%20invokes%20secular%20legal%20principles.%20It%20gives%20land%20to%20the%20party%20representing%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20Virajman.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20recognises%20the%20destruction%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20as%20a%20criminal%20act%20and%20asks%20the%20state%20to%20give%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20mosque.%20Nobody%20is%20talking%20about%20these%20details.%20The%20entire%20political%20class%20gives%20us%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20court%20has%20accepted%20the%20Hindutva%20claim%20and%20for%20that%20reason%20Hindutva%20politics%20is%20invincible.%20The%20Opposition%20wants%20to%20break%20the%20monopoly%20of%20BJP%20on%20Hindutva%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20Ram%20Temple.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Verma%2C%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%20(CPR)%2C%20said%20that%20the%20event%20presents%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdilemma%E2%80%9D%20for%20other%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20go%20there%20it%20is%20a%20problem%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20then%20also%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem.%20That%20is%20why%20it%20is%20a%20dilemma%20for%20them.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20easy%20answer.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20helpful.%20They%20should%20think%20real%20hard%20on%20this%20question%20and%20think%20about%20what%20their%20politics%20on%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%2C%20so%20they%20are%20only%20reacting%20at%20the%20moment.%20Of%20course%20if%20your%20opponent%20is%20in%20a%20dilemma%20it%20helps%20the%20BJP%20but%20only%20time%20will%20tell%20whether%20it%20will%20bring%20votes%20or%20not.%20But%20the%20opposition%20is%20in%20a%20bind%20on%20this%20question%20and%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ahmed%2C%20in%20post%202014%20India%2C%20the%20political%20class%20has%20lost%20interest%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20secularism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20secularism%20has%20become%20irrelevant%20in%20the%20context.%20People%20adhere%20to%20secular%20values%20in%20various%20ways.%20Politically%20speaking%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20to%20use%20the%20Ayodhya%20celebration%20for%202024%20elections.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20the%20party%20is%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20as%20a%20political%20issue.%20There%20is%20a%20serious%20competition%20for%20Hindu%20votes.%20Every%20political%20party%20is%20interested%20in%20capitalising%20on%20Hindu%20sentiments.%20So%20BJP%20is%20not%20the%20only%20party%20which%20will%20use%20Hindutva%20for%20political%20gains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMridula%20Mukherjee%2C%20former%20professor%20of%20history%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20and%20former%20director%20of%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20said%20that%20January%2022%20represents%20a%20new%20turn%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20post-independence%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20about%20the%20prime%20minister%20attending%20the%20event%20but%20it%20is%20much%20more.%20He%20is%20actually%20the%20main%20character%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20he%20is%20performing%20religious%20functions.%20Inaugurating%20a%20temple%20is%20very%20different%20from%20performing%20religious%20functions%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20In%20my%20understanding%20it%20is%20not%20within%20the%20permissible%20framework%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukherjee%20said%20that%20while%20it%20is%20a%20religious%20event%20in%20which%20a%20temple%20is%20being%20consecrated%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20purpose%20to%20which%20it%20is%20being%20put%20is%20clearly%20political%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20classic%20sense%20the%20use%20of%20religion%20for%20political%20gains%20is%20what%20we%20call%20communalism%2C%20whether%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim%20or%20Christian%20or%20Jew.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705847445000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21194322%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.07-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modi-in-ram-temple-pran-prathishtha-end-of-secularism-as-distance-between-state-and-religion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20January%2012%2C%20Modi%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20undertake%2011-day%20rituals%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20and%20said%20that%20God%20had%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20him%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20present%20at%20the%20ceremony.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpm-modi-in-ram-temple-pran-prathishtha-end-of-secularism-as-distance-between-state-and-religion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20World%20with%20Yalda%20Hakim%20-%20Sky%20News%20launches%20new%20foreign%20affairs%20show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705845000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe